name: Economy update
content:
Here's the latest changelog:

**Version 1.0 - Economy Update**
- First version of this bot!
- Bot registers every user on the server it joins
- Every new user joining the server will get automatically registered
- Every user has a profile in a SQLite database
- `$help`, `$give`, `$balance`, `$admins`, `$changelog` commands for everyone
- `$sugive`, `$reset` commands for admins
- `$promote`, `$demote` for super admins
